<exercise>
<statement><p>
<ol marker="a.">
<li><p>
A pole leans against a vertical wall. The pole has length 2, and it touches the wall at height <m>H=1</m>. The pole slides down, still touching the wall, with its height decreasing at a rate of <m>\diff{H}{t}=0.5</m>.
</p>

<sidebyside width="63%">
<image><latex-image>\begin{tikzpicture}
